    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……驚きの頭脳だな……
まだ１３だと言うのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... This is one impressive intellect for a 13 year old 
girl... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえのその頭脳は、
いつか我が国を支える、
偉大な財産となる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you wish, you can use that intelligence of yours for our 
country to help assert a better future. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よく学べ、メルティア。
おまえは私の自慢の娘だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Study well, &lt;MEL&gt;tia. You are my pride and joy. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしは本当の親に
いらないと言われて
捨てられた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My biological parents decided to throw me out to the 
streets. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ずっと、誰かに
必要とされたかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But...I really needed someone. I was a child starving for 
affection. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261308</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、
１３歳のわたしは、
魔科学研究者を志したの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why at the young age of 13 I decided to start my 
studies in Magitechnology. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261652</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そして
魔科学兵器を作ったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And then we created the Mana Cannon. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、お父様に
喜んでいただくため</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes. Anything to make my father happy. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうすれば、
わたしはずっとお父様に
必要とされる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In that case father would always appreciate me. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、わたしには、
いつも恐怖があった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Still, I was scared during all this time. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もし、何もできなくなったら、
わたしはまたいらないって
言われるんじゃないかって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There was nothing I wouldn't do for him so I was at the 
mercy of his expectations. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、必死でがんばったの。
お父様に愛される子でいるために</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why I was so desperate. I needed to stay as father's 
pride and joy. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>5</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当に、そう？
そこまでしなくても、
あなたを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that true? But you've gone as far as to... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたしを
必要としてくれる人は、
他にも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean... there are important people in my life too, yet... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたにはわからない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How would you understand...!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたが妬ましかった。
不必要だと言われることなく、</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I am jealous of you. There's no need for me to say it for 
you to understand. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262596</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>常に何者かに
守られているあなたが</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You always had someone to love you and take care of you. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_320_040_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>わたし、は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
